{"tid":675613,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[升班賽有新圖]17-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合--鄧麗欣 對 岑麗香","createTime":"2018-05-23T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T14:04:38.000Z","uid":92376,"like":86,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1539cb17c320f9f79d9bf90361efc50d53d36a","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鄧麗欣v岑麗香<br />\n<br />\n冠聯全季積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QRzxRlO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQRzxRlO.png&h=40fcce42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-5-24 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Tok4r6J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTok4r6J.png&h=2f24c199&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6q0ECaK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6q0ECaK.png&h=2ab839c3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(7)鄧麗欣vs岑麗香(4)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"be2c22ad2f6ae00f387f2b89d603c6429e20e05f","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b8439f5046ed9a7b69b07a596e3dab272d7372","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"今日屙屎先定屙尿先果種無聊問題就搶住投<br />\n今次冠聯附4強至獨家有得用正負評黎投,好好珍惜啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甲乙組個4強唔會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21629ac1ef74a7e2447ef8d786b1ad8701ff7f3","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"冠聯升班附加賽,將會決定出最後一位升班到18-19超聯既女神席位,可以講係決定一季成敗既最後對決,我諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04374390584872c911abe5fa3091a64911e5fd6","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"暫時賽事開始左13分鐘,兩位選手都係好保守,各入3分"},{"pid":"0b2bb6327707fcf22f2bae34fd9dc5799725a8ee","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"暫時比分係8-10"},{"pid":"51a5add6231ef73ca51f42ce56ba4ea7ce21136b","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef1242873433145cfe7c3fd6607008ee9d688b9","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"9-12"},{"pid":"66933b3d9f7308b79160c0a2961b17f871305b9b","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:42:15.000Z","msg":"9-14"},{"pid":"7bca01c530bc6a92f9d1751b22ddede834908603","tid":675613,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T16:51:06.0